<paragraph id="8B9EA90EFF89D932BEA32D83FB728821" blockId="9.[136,1451,2032,2090]" pageId="9" pageNumber="130">
Prostrate shrub with adventitious roots; young stems with brown barbellate trichomes; petioles 
<quantity id="4CD904EBFF89D932BA0A2D83FB3E880E" box="[1057,1164,2032,2053]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.3" metricValueMax="3.3" metricValueMin="1.3" pageId="9" pageNumber="130" unit="cm" value="2.3" valueMax="3.3" valueMin="1.3">1.3–3.3 cm</quantity>
